Subject: Disable Spotless for the LTR plugin build
Upstream source: https://github.com/opensearch-project/opensearch-learning-to-rank-base/blob/3.6.0/build.gradle
DHI context: https://github.com/docker-hardened-images/definitions-external/tree/main/image/opensearch
Description: The DHI build patches plugin dependencies for CVE remediation.
  Disable Spotless formatting enforcement so patched generated dependency
  files do not fail the plugin build.

--- a/build.gradle
